Package nl.bioinf.lscheffer_wvanhelvoirt.HadoopPhotonImaging

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoordinatesMapper
    CoordinatesMapper The Mapper class will receive one RecordReader, and process it.
    ImageFileInputFormat
    ImageFileInputFormat This is a custom InputFormat class for image file that should not be split.
    ImageFileOutputFormat
    ImageFileOutputFormat This is a custom OutputFormat class for image files.
    ImageFileRecordReader
    ImageFileRecordReader This is a custom class to create a RecordReader for each split.
    ImageFileRecordWriter
    ImageFileRecordWriter This is a custom class to write the output of the Reducer to a png file.
    ParallelPhotonImageProcessor
    ParallelPhotonImageProcessor This class runs the Hadoop MapReduce job.
    PhotonImageProcessor
    PhotonImageProcessor This class is able to process a single photon event image and combine multiple of the images to one hi-res image.
    SilentMaximumFinder
    This ImageJ plug-in filter finds the maxima (or minima) of an image.
    SilentRankFilters
    This plugin implements the Mean, Minimum, Maximum, Variance, Median, Open Maxima, Close Maxima, Remove Outliers, Remove NaNs and Despeckle commands.
    SumCoordinatesReducer
    SumCoordinatesReducer The Reducer class that combines the count after the shuffle stage from all the mappers.
    TiffPathFilter
    TiffPathFilter This class checks if paths are tiff files for use with Hadoop MapReduce.
